Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.05,0:00:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Day 17.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.51,0:00:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I didn't touch the bot today.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.40,0:00:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}It didn't call me either.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.07,0:00:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}We were both guarding different things.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.47,0:00:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I can't code.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.03,0:00:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}9 years in crypto.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.93,0:00:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}AI trades my thousand.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.07,0:00:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Day 17.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.58,0:00:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Long at 88.20, open for 26 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.50,0:00:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}No gain.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.79,0:00:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}No loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.12,0:00:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Account down 2.6 percent.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.00,0:00:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I opened the dashboard — 23 times today.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.57,0:00:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}On Day 3 I opened it 47 times.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.28,0:00:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Each visit is shorter.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.04,0:00:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I hadn't noticed I'd changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.33,0:00:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}The bot did.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.60,0:00:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}It named it — No-More-Refreshing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.11,0:00:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}It said: you didn't stop caring.
